{"tid":550324,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股市原意，乃讓集資搜資有其地，社會向榮，人皆有賺。","createTime":"2018-02-04T16:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T00:36:06.000Z","uid":13663,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e338c300e6f60ec83f1e0377897d384c8ba3197","tid":550324,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"股市原意，乃讓集資搜資有其地，社會向榮，人皆有賺。 惜人性貪婪，耗盡心思，巧取豪奪，樂土成煉獄，血雨腥風，殺戳不息，無數人蕩產傾家輸性命，勝者則喪良知人格。 余於股壇數十載，未嘗見一真正鸁者，智者應知此乃一處永無贏家之戰。 取勝唯一法︰「及早離去」四字而矣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514cc5a6a3476accbc4b99af7735fab3a72692aa","tid":550324,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"用指數ETF就唔會有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70518831f31419628377ef84eaa12f9d8fc9d9ce","tid":550324,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"d9694fc04487c048216b18fb0c3bac85bd8ffbea","tid":550324,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T18:03:26.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過部電腦分析錯誤"},{"pid":"31bbacdf684f4c39eb0cf6349367abdd3d74a4d4","tid":550324,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9694fc04487c048216b18fb0c3bac85bd8ffbea","tid":550324,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T18:03:26.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過部電腦分析錯誤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T00:36:06.000Z","msg":"部電腦只係解碼"}]}